description: Some guys really have strange expectations. The one who came here today for the job-interview graduated from university and didn´t have any work-experience apart from an office-job where he worked a couple of months. And he expected a salary of 25 000 or above. I was quite amused to hear this as he knew it would be a warehouse-job which he is applying for and which is usually not so well-paid. And indeed he was just a pokerface. When I offered him the job for 22 000 CZK I could see from his eyes that he was very interested. And of course he couldn´t pay the one-time registration-fee. He was quite sportive so I wanted to see his body. And he agreed. And when I went on he even sucked me off. But would he let me fuck him?
title: Dirty Scout 25
